Paytrail,is,a,Finnish,online,payment,service,that,aims,to,help,companies,provide,a,pleasant,shopping,experience,for,their,customers,The,service,allows,customers,to,make,purchases,using,their,preferred,payment,method,whether,it,is,online,bank,payments,card,payments,invoicing,or,installments,Paytrail,also,offers,an,account,for,consumers,that,allows,them,to,use,one,login,for,all,their,online,purchases,The,Paytrail,Connect,REST,API,offers,programmatic,access,to,Paytrail,services,An,account,with,service,is,required